<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="robots" content="index, follow" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">

    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/img/favicon.png">
    <title>Mineshare | Форум</title>

    <meta property="og:title" content="Mineshare | Форум" />
    <meta property="og:image" content="https://mineshare.top/img/favicon-alt.png">

    <link href="https://fonts.cdnfonts.com/css/tt-norms-pro" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" media="screen" href="https://fontlibrary.org//face/tt-norms-medium" type="text/css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://kit.fontawesome.com/7a9092486b.css" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link type="text/css" rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" media="screen,projection">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.3/dist/css/bootstrap-grid.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link
        href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Nunito+Sans:ital,opsz,wght@0,6..12,200..1000;1,6..12,200..1000&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet">
</head>

<body>
    <style>
        body {
            height: 100vh;
            background: #fff;
            background: url('../img/cloud-bg.png') repeat-x 0 / 90% auto;
            height: 100px;
            animation: cloud-bg 60s linear infinite;
            margin: 0;
        }

        @keyframes cloud-bg {
            0% {
                background-position: 0 -100px;
            }

            100% {
                background-position: 100vw -100px;
            }
        }

        nav .navbar {
            height: 95px;
            position: relative;
            background: white;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding-left: 30px;
            padding-right: 30px;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }

        nav .navbar .logo {
            margin-top: 27px;
        }

        nav .navbar .logo a {
            color: #000;
            font-family: 'TT Norms Pro', sans-serif;
            text-transform: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 28px;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        nav .navbar .search {
            height: 50px;
            background: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding-left: 10px;
            padding-right: 10px;
            margin-top: 22.5px;
            margin-right: 12px;
            vertical-align: top;
        }

        nav .navbar .search input {
            height: 34px;
            border: none;
            font-family: 'TT Norms Pro', sans-serif;
            vertical-align: top;
            margin-top: 6px;
        }

        nav .navbar .search input:focus {
            outline: none;
        }

        nav .navbar .search button {
            width: 32px;
            height: 32px;
            position: relative;
            background: #11B2FF;
            border-radius: 6px;
            border: none;
            vertical-align: top;
            margin-top: 9px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        nav .navbar .search button i {
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            color: #fff;
        }

        nav .navbar .auth button {
            width: 150px;
            height: 50px;
            background: linear-gradient(98.44deg, #8DEBFF 0%, #00ABFF 100%), #339DFF;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(113, 212, 255, 0.7);
            border-radius: 10px;
            border: none;
            font-size: 19px;
            color: #fff;
            font-family: 'TTNormsMedium';
            font-size: 19px;
            padding-bottom: 4px;
            margin-top: 22.5px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .card {
            min-height: 600px;
            position: relative;
            background-color: #F3F7FC;
            border-radius: 18px;
            padding-top: 25px;
            padding-left: 25px;
            padding-right: 25px;
            padding-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .global-title {
            width: calc(100% - 160px);
            position: relative;
            color: rgb(198, 198, 198);
            font-family: 'TT Norms Pro', sans-serif;
            font-size: 26px;
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-left: 5px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .global-title::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 55%;
            right: 0;
            width: calc(100% - 300px);
            height: 2px;
            background: rgb(202, 202, 202);
            border-radius: 40px;
        }

        .topic-add {
            width: 140px;
            height: 40px;
            position: relative;
            background: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0px 2px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            border-radius: 10px;
            border: none;
            color: #3A4E57;
            font-family: 'TT Norms Pro', sans-serif;
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
            padding-left: 10px;
            padding-bottom: 2px;
            margin-top: -2px;
            cursor: pointer;
            user-select: none;
        }

        .topic-add:hover {
            color: #11B2FF;
        }

        .topic-add i {
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-left: 5px;
        }

        .topic {
            position: relative;
            background: #fff;
            background-size: 400px;
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-position: 100%;
            box-shadow: 0px 2px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            padding-left: 20px;
            padding-right: 20px;
            padding-bottom: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            cursor: pointer;
            user-select: none;
        }

        .line {
            width: 100%;
            height: 2px;
            border-radius: 40px;
            background: rgb(202, 202, 202);
            margin-top: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .topic:hover .title {
            color: #11B2FF;
        }

        .topic .avatar {
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            position: relative;
            background: #11B2FF;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }

        .topic .avatar i {
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 24px;
        }

        .topic .title-subtitle {
            height: 50px;
            vertical-align: top;
        }

        .topic .title {
            color: #3A4E57;
            font-family: 'TT Norms Pro', sans-serif;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-top: -1px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .topic .subtitle {
            width: 400px;
            height: 25px;
            color: #959595;
            font-family: 'TT Norms Pro', sans-serif;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 400;
            line-height: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .topic .counter {
            height: 52.5px;
            overflow: hidden;
            vertical-align: top;
            float: right;
        }

        .topic .counter .records {
            height: 22px;
            background: #fff;
            border: 1.5px solid #ededed;
            border-radius: 4px;
            color: #9c9c9c;
            font-family: 'TT Norms Pro', sans-serif;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 500;
            text-align: right;
            padding-top: 2px;
            padding-left: 10px;
            padding-right: 10px;
            padding-bottom: 2px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .topic .counter .records i {
            font-size: 10px;
            vertical-align: top;
            margin-top: 3.5px;
            margin-left: 5px;
        }

        .topic .counter .views {
            height: 22px;
            background: #fff;
            border: 1.5px solid #ededed;
            border-radius: 4px;
            color: #9c9c9c;
            font-family: 'TT Norms Pro', sans-serif;
            font-size: 13px;
            text-align: right;
            font-weight: 500;
            padding-top: 2px;
            padding-left: 10px;
            padding-right: 10px;
            padding-bottom: 2px;
        }

        .topic .counter .views i {
            font-size: 10px;
            vertical-align: top;
            margin-top: 3px;
            margin-left: 3px;
        }

        .topic .date-status {
            height: 52.5px;
            overflow: hidden;
            vertical-align: top;
            float: right;
            margin-right: 7px;
        }

        .topic .date-status .date {
            height: 22px;
            background: #fff;
            border: 1.5px solid #ededed;
            border-radius: 4px;
            color: #9c9c9c;
            font-family: 'TT Norms Pro', sans-serif;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 500;
            text-align: right;
            padding-top: 2px;
            padding-left: 10px;
            padding-right: 10px;
            padding-bottom: 2px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .topic .date-status .date i {
            font-size: 10px;
            vertical-align: top;
            margin-top: 3.5px;
            margin-left: 5px;
        }

        .topic .date-status .status {
            height: 22px;
            background: #fff;
            border: 1.5px solid #ededed;
            border-radius: 4px;
            color: #fff;
            font-family: 'TT Norms Pro', sans-serif;
            font-size: 13px;
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: 500;
            padding-top: 2px;
            padding-left: 10px;
            padding-right: 10px;
            padding-bottom: 2px;
        }

        .topic .date-status .status i {
            font-size: 10px;
            vertical-align: top;
            margin-top: 3px;
            margin-left: 5px;
        }

        .topic .info {
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            position: relative;
            background: #fff;
            border: 1.5px solid #ededed;
            border-radius: 4px;
            float: right;
            margin-left: 7px;
            transition: 0.2s;
        }

        .topic .info:hover {
            border: 1.5px solid #11B2FF;
        }

        .topic .info i {
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            color: #11B2FF;
            font-size: 20px;
        }

        .topic .user {
            height: 50px;
            position: relative;
            background: #fff;
            border: 1.5px solid #ededed;
            border-radius: 4px;
            float: right;
            margin-left: 7px;
        }

        .topic .user img {
            width: 34px;
            height: 34px;
            position: relative;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin-top: 8px;
            margin-left: 12px;
            margin-right: 4px;
        }

        .topic .user .username-time {
            margin-top: 7px;
            margin-right: 13px;
            vertical-align: top;
        }

        .topic .user .username {
            color: #9c9c9c;
            font-family: 'TT Norms Pro', sans-serif;
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-bottom: 2px;
        }

        .topic .user .time {
            color: #b9b9b9;
            font-family: 'TT Norms Pro', sans-serif;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        footer {
            background: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0px -3px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            padding-top: 40px;
            padding-bottom: 25px;
            margin-top: 50px;
        }

        footer .group {
            color: #3A4E57;
            font-family: 'TT Norms Pro', sans-serif;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        footer .link {
            font-family: "Nunito Sans", sans-serif;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        footer .link a {
            color: #808080;
        }

        footer .link a:hover {
            color: #11B2FF;
        }

        footer .discord {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            position: relative;
            background: #7289da;
            border: 2px solid #7289da;
            border-radius: 8px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        footer .discord:hover {
            border: 2px solid #11B2FF;
        }

        footer .discord i {
            position: absolute;
            top: 49%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
    </style>

    <nav>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="navbar">
                <div class="d-flex justify-content-between">
                    <div class="logo">
                        <a href="/">Mineshare<span style="color: #bdbdbe; font-weight: 500;">｜ФОРУМ</span></a>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <div class="d-inline-flex search">
                            <form>
                                <input name="search" type="text" placeholder="Мини-игры..">
                                <button><i class="fa-solid fa-magnifying-glass"></i></button>
                            </form>
                        </div>

                        <div class="d-inline-flex auth">
                            <% if (user) { %>
                                <button>Кабинет</button>
                                <% } else { %>
                                    <button onclick="window.location = '/login';">Войти</button>
                                    <% } %>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div style="margin-top: 40px;">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row g-4">
                <div class="col-12">
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between">
                            <p class="global-title">Набор и поиск команды</p>
                            <button class="topic-add" onclick="window.location = '/teams/add';">Добавить<i class="fa-solid fa-rectangle-history-circle-plus"></i></button>
                        </div>
                        

                        <% topics.forEach(topic=> { %>

                            <div class="topic" onclick="window.location = '/teams/topic/<%= topic.identifier %>';">
                                <div class="d-inline-flex avatar">
                                    <% if (topic.type==1) { %>
                                        <i class="fa-solid fa-users-medical"></i>
                                        <% } else if (topic.type==2) { %>
                                            <i class="fa-solid fa-user-plus"></i>
                                            <% } %>
                                </div>
                                <div class="d-inline-flex flex-column title-subtitle"
                                    onclick="window.location = '/teams';">
                                    <div class="title">
                                        <%= topic.title %>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="subtitle">
                                        <%= topic.description %>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <% if(topic.status == false) { %>
                                <div class="d-inline-flex info"><i class="fa-solid fa-lock-open"></i></div>
                                <% } else { %>
                                    <div class="d-inline-flex info"><i class="fa-solid fa-lock"></i></div>
                                    <% } %>

                                <div class="user">
                                    <img
                                        src="https://crafatar.com/avatars/<%= topic.skin %>?default=54c32ed5ab7243e5a00eec680d514523">
                                    <div class="d-inline-flex flex-column username-time">
                                        <div class="d-inline-flex username">
                                            <%= topic.username %>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="d-inline-flex time"><%= topic.lastOnline %></div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <div class="d-inline-flex flex-column counter">
                                    <div class="records">∞<i class="fa-solid fa-message-lines"></i></div>
                                    <div class="views">∞<i class="fa-solid fa-eye"></i></div>
                                </div>

                                <div class="d-inline-flex flex-column date-status">
                                    <div class="date"><%= topic.update %><i class="fa-solid fa-clock"></i></div>
                                    <div class="status"><i class="fa-solid fa-lock-open"></i></div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <% }); %>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>


    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-12">
                    <div class="d-flex justify-content-between">
                        <div>
                            <div class="group">Ссылки</div>
                            <div class="link"><a>Команда разработчиков</a></div>
                            <div class="link"><a>Подробности проекта</a></div>
                        </div>

                        <div>
                            <div class="group">Информация</div>
                            <div class="link"><a>Условия использования</a></div>
                            <div class="link"><a>Политика конфиденциальности</a></div>
                        </div>

                        <div>
                            <div class="group">Услуги</div>
                            <div class="link"><a>Партнёрские программы</a></div>
                            <div class="link"><a>Магазин мониторинга</a></div>
                        </div>

                        <div>
                            <div class="group">Помощь</div>
                            <div class="link"><a>Техническая поддержка</a></div>
                            <div class="link"><a>Сообщить о нарушении</a></div>
                        </div>

                        <div>
                            <div class="discord" onclick="window.open('https://discord.gg/mineshare', '_blank')"><i
                                    class="fa-brands fa-discord"></i></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
    </footer>
</body>

</html>